sequenceDiagram
    participant DSP as Data Science Pipelines<br/>(DSP)
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/TCP or 5432/TCP

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Metadata Recording

    DSP->>MLMD: PutExecutionType(request)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT INTO Type ...<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL protocol, Optional SSL
    DB-->>MLMD: OK (type_id)
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutExecutionTypeResponse(type_id)

    DSP->>MLMD: PutExecution(request)<br/>execution + artifacts + events + contexts
    MLMD->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION<br/>INSERT execution, artifacts, events
    DB-->>MLMD: OK (ids)
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutExecutionResponse(ids)

    DSP->>MLMD: PutArtifacts(request)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE Artifact ...<br/>Optional SSL, Username/password auth
    DB-->>MLMD: OK (artifact_ids)
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutArtifactsResponse(artifact_ids)

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 2: Lineage Query

    participant UI as Pipeline UI /<br/>DSP Component

    UI->>MLMD: GetLineageSubgraph(request)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT ... JOIN ... (graph traversal)<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL protocol, Optional SSL
    DB-->>MLMD: Result set (nodes, edges)
    MLMD-->>UI: GetLineageSubgraphResponse<br/>artifacts, executions, contexts, events
